OL,3,C2025 has been the UK's sunniest year,
OL,4,Chelping smash solar power records
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Senior Producer
OL,7,FRhiannon Hopley
OL,9,FThe UK has officially had its sunniest
OL,10,Fyear since records began.
OL,12,FThe Met Office said there were 1,622
OL,13,Fhours of sunshine in 2025 so far,
OL,14,Fbeating the previous sunniest year,
OL,15,Fwhich was 2003.
OL,17,FThe records go back to 1910.
