OL,3,C2025 has been the UK's sunniest year,
OL,4,Chelping smash solar power records
OL,6,FBreaking it down by nation, with only
OL,7,Fa few weeks to go, England has already
OL,8,Fhad its sunniest year on record, while
OL,9,FScotland has had its second sunniest.
OL,11,FWales is having its sixth sunniest
OL,12,Fyear.
OL,14,FIn Northern Ireland, it has been less
OL,15,Fsunny, but with two weeks to go in
OL,16,F2025, it could potentially reach the
OL,17,Ftop ten.
