OL,3,C2025 has been the UK's sunniest year,
OL,4,Chelping smash solar power records
OL,6,FThe UK has become much sunnier since
OL,7,Fthe 1980s, but the cause of this trend
OL,8,Fis uncertain. It could be down to
OL,9,Fnatural variability or even reduced
OL,10,Faerosols.
OL,12,FClimate projections currently show no
OL,13,Fdefinitive evidence of a future trend
OL,14,Fin sunshine amounts due to climate
OL,15,Fchange.
OL,17,FIndeed, we are seeing quite a lot of
OL,18,Fvariability between years. While 2025
OL,19,Fmay have been the sunniest on record,
OL,20,Flast year was actually the dullest
OL,21,Fyear since 1998.
