OL,3,C2025 has been the UK's sunniest year,
OL,4,Chelping smash solar power records
OL,6,FThis year's surplus of sunshine has
OL,7,Fhad knock-on effects for power
OL,8,Fgeneration.
OL,10,FA record 6.3% of the UK's energy mix
OL,11,Fcame from solar power in 2025 - a 30%
OL,12,Frise from last year, according to
OL,13,FSolar Energy UK.
OL,15,FIt is estimated that 18,314 gigawatt-
OL,16,Fhours of sun-powered electricity have
OL,17,Fbeen generated so far this year -
OL,18,Fenough to make over 732 billion cups
OL,19,Fof tea.
