OL,11,FThe rise is due to a mix of more sunny
OL,12,Fhours and an 18% surge in capacity
OL,13,Fthis year.
OL,15,FChris Hewett, the Chief Executive of
OL,16,FSolar Energy UK, said: "The growth of
OL,17,Fsolar this year in the UK has been
OL,18,Fdown to it being particularly sunny
OL,19,Fyear but also due to the building of
OL,20,Fsolar on roofs and solar farms, which
OL,21,Fhas driven that rise.
