OL,3,C2025 has been the UK's sunniest year,
OL,4,Chelping smash solar power records
OL,6,F"There's clearly a market - the
OL,7,Frooftop solar industry in the UK has
OL,8,Fgrown more this year than in any other
OL,9,Fyear previously. Quarter of a million
OL,10,Fsmall businesses and homes have put
OL,11,Fsolar on their roof this year.
OL,13,F"If you have solar on your roof, this
OL,14,Fyear's energy prices will have been
OL,15,Flower for you. It is also driving down
OL,16,Fthe price of wholesale energy, meaning
OL,17,Flower bills for everyone.
