OL,3,C2025 has been the UK's sunniest year,
OL,4,Chelping smash solar power records
OL,6,FCurrently, it accounts for 6.5% of all
OL,7,Fenergy generation this year. Because
OL,8,Fwe are expecting growth to continue to
OL,9,Fbe strong, that could be 15-20% by the
OL,10,Fend of this decade - meaning solar
OL,11,Fwould exceed the amount of power
OL,12,Fcurrently being delivered by nuclear."
